<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Server Error</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .idea-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .idea-text {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        a {
            background: #fff;
            color: #ef4444;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 7px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 5rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .idea-text {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1>500</h1>
        <h2>Something Went Wrong</h2>
        <p>This idea was so stupid, it broke the internet!</p>

        <div class="idea-box">
            <p class="idea-text">
                "A server that only works when nobody's looking at it"
            </p>
        </div>

        <a href="/">Try Again</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
